{
  "video_id": "X9FFzWUInyA",
  "title": "Gr√©goire Courtine: The paralyzed rat that walked",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12446.0,
      "end_time": 14710.0,
      "text": "I am a neuroscientist"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14710.0,
      "end_time": 17881.0,
      "text": "with a mixed background in physics and medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17882.0,
      "end_time": 22923.0,
      "text": "My lab at the Swiss Federal Institute of Technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22923.0,
      "end_time": 26113.0,
      "text": "focuses on spinal cord injury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26113.0,
      "end_time": 28844.0,
      "text": "which affects more than 50,000 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28844.0,
      "end_time": 31534.0,
      "text": "around the world every year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31534.0,
      "end_time": 35140.0,
      "text": "with dramatic consequences for affected individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35140.0,
      "end_time": 37373.0,
      "text": "whose life literally shatters"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37373.0,
      "end_time": 40608.0,
      "text": "in a matter of a handful of seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40608.0,
      "end_time": 43666.0,
      "text": "And for me, the Man of Steel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43666.0,
      "end_time": 45870.0,
      "text": "Christopher Reeve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45870.0,
      "end_time": 47959.0,
      "text": "has best raised the awareness"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47960.0,
      "end_time": 50875.0,
      "text": "on the distress of spinal cord injured people."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50875.0,
      "end_time": 54140.0,
      "text": "And this is how I started my own personal journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54140.0,
      "end_time": 55513.0,
      "text": "in this field of research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55513.0,
      "end_time": 58949.0,
      "text": "working with the Christopher and Dana Reeve Foundation."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58950.0,
      "end_time": 63546.0,
      "text": "I still remember this decisive moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63546.0,
      "end_time": 65497.0,
      "text": "It was just at the end of a regular day of work"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65497.0,
      "end_time": 67400.0,
      "text": "with the foundation."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67400.0,
      "end_time": 71692.0,
      "text": "Chris addressed us, the scientists and experts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71692.0,
      "end_time": 75285.0,
      "text": "\"You have to be more pragmatic."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75285.0,
      "end_time": 77637.0,
      "text": "When leaving your laboratory tomorrow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77637.0,
      "end_time": 80541.0,
      "text": "I want you to stop by the rehabilitation center"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80541.0,
      "end_time": 82149.0,
      "text": "to watch injured people"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82150.0,
      "end_time": 84175.0,
      "text": "fighting to take a step,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84175.0,
      "end_time": 86816.0,
      "text": "struggling to maintain their trunk."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86816.0,
      "end_time": 88229.0,
      "text": "And when you go home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88229.0,
      "end_time": 90639.0,
      "text": "think of what you are going to change in your research"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90639.0,
      "end_time": 94207.0,
      "text": "on the following day to make their lives better.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94207.0,
      "end_time": 98259.0,
      "text": "These words, they stuck with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100651.0,
      "text": "This was more than 10 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100651.0,
      "end_time": 103417.0,
      "text": "but ever since, my laboratory has followed"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103418.0,
      "end_time": 105381.0,
      "text": "the pragmatic approach to recovery"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105381.0,
      "end_time": 107792.0,
      "text": "after spinal cord injury."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107792.0,
      "end_time": 109833.0,
      "text": "And my first step in this direction"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109833.0,
      "end_time": 113122.0,
      "text": "was to develop a new model of spinal cord injury"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113122.0,
      "end_time": 116769.0,
      "text": "that would more closely mimic some of the key features of human injury"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116769.0,
      "end_time": 120141.0,
      "text": "while offering well-controlled experimental conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120141.0,
      "end_time": 122708.0,
      "text": "And for this purpose, we placed two hemisections"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 122708.0,
      "end_time": 124123.0,
      "text": "on opposite sides of the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124123.0,
      "end_time": 126268.0,
      "text": "They completely interrupt the communication"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 126268.0,
      "end_time": 128850.0,
      "text": "between the brain and the spinal cord,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 128850.0,
      "end_time": 131560.0,
      "text": "thus leading to complete and permanent paralysis"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131560.0,
      "end_time": 133327.0,
      "text": "of the leg."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 133327.0,
      "end_time": 137218.0,
      "text": "But, as observed, after most injuries in humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 137218.0,
      "end_time": 140167.0,
      "text": "there is this intervening gap of intact neural tissue"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140168.0,
      "end_time": 142871.0,
      "text": "through which recovery can occur."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 142871.0,
      "end_time": 145912.0,
      "text": "But how to make it happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145912.0,
      "end_time": 149273.0,
      "text": "Well, the classical approach"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149273.0,
      "end_time": 151909.0,
      "text": "consists of applying intervention"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 151909.0,
      "end_time": 154819.0,
      "text": "that would promote the growth of the severed fiber"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154819.0,
      "end_time": 156927.0,
      "text": "to the original target."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156927.0,
      "end_time": 160678.0,
      "text": "And while this certainly remained the key for a cure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160678.0,
      "end_time": 164192.0,
      "text": "this seemed extraordinarily complicated to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164193.0,
      "end_time": 166918.0,
      "text": "To reach clinical fruition rapidly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166918.0,
      "end_time": 168478.0,
      "text": "it was obvious:"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168478.0,
      "end_time": 172398.0,
      "text": "I had to think about the problem differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 172398.0,
      "end_time": 175506.0,
      "text": "It turned out that more than 100 years of research"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175506.0,
      "end_time": 177147.0,
      "text": "on spinal cord physiology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177147.0,
      "end_time": 179471.0,
      "text": "starting with the Nobel Prize Sherrington,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 179472.0,
      "end_time": 181279.0,
      "text": "had shown that"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 181279.0,
      "end_time": 183514.0,
      "text": "the spinal cord, below most injuries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 183514.0,
      "end_time": 186767.0,
      "text": "contained all the necessary and sufficient neural networks"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 186767.0,
      "end_time": 189870.0,
      "text": "to coordinate locomotion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189870.0,
      "end_time": 192460.0,
      "text": "but because input from the brain is interrupted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 192460.0,
      "end_time": 195214.0,
      "text": "they are in a nonfunctional state, like kind of dormant."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 195214.0,
      "end_time": 199546.0,
      "text": "My idea: We awaken this network."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 199546.0,
      "end_time": 203833.0,
      "text": "And at the time, I was a post-doctoral fellow in Los Angeles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 203833.0,
      "end_time": 206399.0,
      "text": "after completing my Ph.D. in France,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 206399.0,
      "end_time": 208308.0,
      "text": "where independent thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 208308.0,
      "end_time": 211415.0,
      "text": "is not necessarily promoted."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 211415.0,
      "end_time": 213242.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 213242.0,
      "end_time": 216995.0,
      "text": "I was afraid to talk to my new boss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 216995.0,
      "end_time": 219388.0,
      "text": "but decided to muster up my courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 219388.0,
      "end_time": 222450.0,
      "text": "I knocked at the door of my wonderful advisor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 222450.0,
      "end_time": 226360.0,
      "text": "Reggie Edgerton, to share my new idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 226360.0,
      "end_time": 228286.0,
      "text": "He listened to me carefully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 228286.0,
      "end_time": 231227.0,
      "text": "and responded with a grin."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 231227.0,
      "end_time": 233270.0,
      "text": "\"Why don&#39;t you try?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 233270.0,
      "end_time": 235395.0,
      "text": "And I promise to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 235395.0,
      "end_time": 238750.0,
      "text": "this was such an important moment in my career,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 238750.0,
      "end_time": 241185.0,
      "text": "when I realized that the great leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 241185.0,
      "end_time": 244178.0,
      "text": "believed in young people and new ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 244178.0,
      "end_time": 245786.0,
      "text": "And this was the idea:"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 245786.0,
      "end_time": 248452.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to use a simplistic metaphor"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 248452.0,
      "end_time": 250578.0,
      "text": "to explain to you this complicated concept."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 250578.0,
      "end_time": 255344.0,
      "text": "Imagine that the locomotor system is a car."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 255344.0,
      "end_time": 257589.0,
      "text": "The engine is the spinal cord."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 257589.0,
      "end_time": 260847.0,
      "text": "The transmission is interrupted. The engine is turned off."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 260848.0,
      "end_time": 263855.0,
      "text": "How could we re-engage the engine?"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 263855.0,
      "end_time": 266997.0,
      "text": "First, we have to provide the fuel;"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 266997.0,
      "end_time": 269340.0,
      "text": "second, press the accelerator pedal;"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 269340.0,
      "end_time": 271277.0,
      "text": "third, steer the car."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 271278.0,
      "end_time": 273400.0,
      "text": "It turned out that there are known neural pathways"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 273400.0,
      "end_time": 275994.0,
      "text": "coming from the brain that play this very function"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 275994.0,
      "end_time": 277376.0,
      "text": "during locomotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 277376.0,
      "end_time": 280900.0,
      "text": "My idea: Replace this missing input"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 280910.0,
      "end_time": 281493.0,
      "text": "to provide the spinal cord"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 281493.0,
      "end_time": 282889.0,
      "text": "with the kind of intervention"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 282889.0,
      "end_time": 287619.0,
      "text": "that the brain would deliver naturally in order to walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 287619.0,
      "end_time": 292580.0,
      "text": "For this, I leveraged 20 years of past research in neuroscience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 292580.0,
      "end_time": 294822.0,
      "text": "first to replace the missing fuel"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 294822.0,
      "end_time": 296890.0,
      "text": "with pharmacological agents"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 296890.0,
      "end_time": 300370.0,
      "text": "that prepare the neurons in the spinal cord to fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 300370.0,
      "end_time": 304425.0,
      "text": "and second, to mimic the accelerator pedal"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 304425.0,
      "end_time": 305905.0,
      "text": "with electrical stimulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 305905.0,
      "end_time": 308730.0,
      "text": "So here imagine an electrode"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 308740.0,
      "end_time": 310480.0,
      "text": "implanted on the back of the spinal cord"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 310480.0,
      "end_time": 312742.0,
      "text": "to deliver painless stimulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 312742.0,
      "end_time": 315574.0,
      "text": "It took many years, but eventually we developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 315574.0,
      "end_time": 318131.0,
      "text": "an electrochemical neuroprosthesis"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 318131.0,
      "end_time": 319897.0,
      "text": "that transformed the neural network"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 319897.0,
      "end_time": 324903.0,
      "text": "in the spinal cord from dormant to a highly functional state."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 324903.0,
      "end_time": 331183.0,
      "text": "Immediately, the paralyzed rat can stand."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 331183.0,
      "end_time": 333510.0,
      "text": "As soon as the treadmill belt starts moving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 333510.0,
      "end_time": 337316.0,
      "text": "the animal shows coordinated movement of the leg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 337316.0,
      "end_time": 339294.0,
      "text": "but without the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 339294.0,
      "end_time": 341284.0,
      "text": "Here what I call \"the spinal brain\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 341284.0,
      "end_time": 344406.0,
      "text": "cognitively processes sensory information"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 344406.0,
      "end_time": 346301.0,
      "text": "arising from the moving leg"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 346301.0,
      "end_time": 349996.0,
      "text": "and makes decisions as to how to activate the muscle"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 349996.0,
      "end_time": 353385.0,
      "text": "in order to stand, to walk, to run,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 353386.0,
      "end_time": 355498.0,
      "text": "and even here, while sprinting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 355498.0,
      "end_time": 357795.0,
      "text": "instantly stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 357795.0,
      "end_time": 360258.0,
      "text": "if the treadmill stops moving."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 360258.0,
      "end_time": 361594.0,
      "text": "This was amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 361595.0,
      "end_time": 364982.0,
      "text": "I was completely fascinated by this locomotion"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 364982.0,
      "end_time": 367477.0,
      "text": "without the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 367477.0,
      "end_time": 371131.0,
      "text": "but at the same time so frustrated."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 371132.0,
      "end_time": 373525.0,
      "text": "This locomotion was completely involuntary."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 373525.0,
      "end_time": 376890.0,
      "text": "The animal had virtually no control over the legs."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 376890.0,
      "end_time": 381100.0,
      "text": "Clearly, the steering system was missing."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 381100.0,
      "end_time": 382902.0,
      "text": "And it then became obvious from me"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 382902.0,
      "end_time": 384250.0,
      "text": "that we had to move away"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 384250.0,
      "end_time": 387622.0,
      "text": "from the classical rehabilitation paradigm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 387622.0,
      "end_time": 389344.0,
      "text": "stepping on a treadmill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 389344.0,
      "end_time": 392564.0,
      "text": "and develop conditions that would encourage"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 392564.0,
      "end_time": 397797.0,
      "text": "the brain to begin voluntary control over the leg."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 397797.0,
      "end_time": 401182.0,
      "text": "With this in mind, we developed a completely new"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 401182.0,
      "end_time": 404412.0,
      "text": "robotic system to support the rat"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 404412.0,
      "end_time": 406938.0,
      "text": "in any direction of space."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 406938.0,
      "end_time": 409113.0,
      "text": "Imagine, this is really cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 409113.0,
      "end_time": 412944.0,
      "text": "So imagine the little 200-gram rat"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 412944.0,
      "end_time": 416645.0,
      "text": "attached at the extremity of this 200-kilo robot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 416645.0,
      "end_time": 419217.0,
      "text": "but the rat does not feel the robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 419217.0,
      "end_time": 421289.0,
      "text": "The robot is transparent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 421289.0,
      "end_time": 423651.0,
      "text": "just like you would hold a young child"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 423651.0,
      "end_time": 426150.0,
      "text": "during the first insecure steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 426150.0,
      "end_time": 429568.0,
      "text": "Let me summarize: The rat received"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 429569.0,
      "end_time": 432140.0,
      "text": "a paralyzing lesion of the spinal cord."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 432140.0,
      "end_time": 434604.0,
      "text": "The electrochemical neuroprosthesis enabled"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 434604.0,
      "end_time": 438811.0,
      "text": "a highly functional state of the spinal locomotor networks."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 438811.0,
      "end_time": 442577.0,
      "text": "The robot provided the safe environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 442577.0,
      "end_time": 444540.0,
      "text": "to allow the rat to attempt anything"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 444540.0,
      "end_time": 447222.0,
      "text": "to engage the paralyzed legs."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 447222.0,
      "end_time": 450460.0,
      "text": "And for motivation, we used what I think"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 450470.0,
      "end_time": 453881.0,
      "text": "is the most powerful pharmacology of Switzerland:"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 453881.0,
      "end_time": 456188.0,
      "text": "fine Swiss chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 456188.0,
      "end_time": 459110.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 459110.0,
      "end_time": 463673.0,
      "text": "Actually, the first results were very, very,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 463673.0,
      "end_time": 466308.0,
      "text": "very disappointing."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 466308.0,
      "end_time": 469610.0,
      "text": "Here is my best physical therapist"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 476794.0,
      "end_time": 479383.0,
      "text": "completely failing to encourage the rat"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 479384.0,
      "end_time": 481445.0,
      "text": "to take a single step,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 481445.0,
      "end_time": 484291.0,
      "text": "whereas the same rat, five minutes earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 484291.0,
      "end_time": 486597.0,
      "text": "walked beautifully on the treadmill."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 486597.0,
      "end_time": 488753.0,
      "text": "We were so frustrated."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 488754.0,
      "end_time": 491653.0,
      "text": "But you know, one of the most essential qualities"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 491653.0,
      "end_time": 494129.0,
      "text": "of a scientist is perseverance."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 494129.0,
      "end_time": 497545.0,
      "text": "We insisted. We refined our paradigm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 497545.0,
      "end_time": 499808.0,
      "text": "and after several months of training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 499808.0,
      "end_time": 503614.0,
      "text": "the otherwise paralyzed rat could stand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 503614.0,
      "end_time": 505426.0,
      "text": "and whenever she decided,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 505426.0,
      "end_time": 507758.0,
      "text": "initiated full weight-bearing locomotion"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 507758.0,
      "end_time": 511800.0,
      "text": "to sprint towards the rewards."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 511800.0,
      "end_time": 514413.0,
      "text": "This is the first recovery ever observed"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 514413.0,
      "end_time": 516307.0,
      "text": "of voluntary leg movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 516307.0,
      "end_time": 518760.0,
      "text": "after an experimental lesion of the spinal cord"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 518760.0,
      "end_time": 522222.0,
      "text": "leading to complete and permanent paralysis."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 522222.0,
      "end_time": 524208.0,
      "text": "In fact --"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 524207.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525929.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 525929.0,
      "end_time": 530308.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 530308.0,
      "end_time": 533402.0,
      "text": "In fact, not only could the rat initiate"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 533402.0,
      "end_time": 536790.0,
      "text": "and sustain locomotion on the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 536790.0,
      "end_time": 538359.0,
      "text": "they could even adjust leg movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 538360.0,
      "end_time": 540716.0,
      "text": "for example, to resist gravity"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 540716.0,
      "end_time": 543340.0,
      "text": "in order to climb a staircase."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 543340.0,
      "end_time": 545290.0,
      "text": "I can promise you this was"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 545290.0,
      "end_time": 548399.0,
      "text": "such an emotional moment in my laboratory."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 548399.0,
      "end_time": 551142.0,
      "text": "It took us 10 years of hard work"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 551142.0,
      "end_time": 553593.0,
      "text": "to reach this goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 553593.0,
      "end_time": 556144.0,
      "text": "But the remaining question was, how?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 556144.0,
      "end_time": 557836.0,
      "text": "I mean, how is it possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 557836.0,
      "end_time": 559514.0,
      "text": "And here, what we found"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 559514.0,
      "end_time": 563190.0,
      "text": "was completely unexpected."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 563190.0,
      "end_time": 567348.0,
      "text": "This novel training paradigm"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 567348.0,
      "end_time": 571190.0,
      "text": "encouraged the brain to create new connections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 571190.0,
      "end_time": 573921.0,
      "text": "some relay circuits"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 573921.0,
      "end_time": 576969.0,
      "text": "that relay information from the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 576969.0,
      "end_time": 580125.0,
      "text": "past the injury and restore cortical control"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 580125.0,
      "end_time": 583566.0,
      "text": "over the locomotor networks below the injury."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 583566.0,
      "end_time": 586488.0,
      "text": "And here, you can see one such example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 586488.0,
      "end_time": 589851.0,
      "text": "where we label the fibers coming from the brain in red."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 589851.0,
      "end_time": 593271.0,
      "text": "This blue neuron is connected with the locomotor center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 593271.0,
      "end_time": 595634.0,
      "text": "and what this constellation"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 595634.0,
      "end_time": 597985.0,
      "text": "of synaptic contacts means"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 597985.0,
      "end_time": 601784.0,
      "text": "is that the brain is reconnected with the locomotor center"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 601784.0,
      "end_time": 605782.0,
      "text": "with only one relay neuron."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 605782.0,
      "end_time": 607713.0,
      "text": "But the remodeling was not restricted"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 607713.0,
      "end_time": 608800.0,
      "text": "to the lesion area."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 608800.0,
      "end_time": 612890.0,
      "text": "It occurred throughout the central nervous system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 612890.0,
      "end_time": 614407.0,
      "text": "including in the brain stem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 614407.0,
      "end_time": 617669.0,
      "text": "where we observed up to 300-percent increase"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 617669.0,
      "end_time": 621428.0,
      "text": "in the density of fibers coming from the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 621428.0,
      "end_time": 624955.0,
      "text": "We did not aim to repair the spinal cord,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 624955.0,
      "end_time": 627552.0,
      "text": "yet we were able to promote"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 627552.0,
      "end_time": 629709.0,
      "text": "one of the more extensive remodeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 629709.0,
      "end_time": 632178.0,
      "text": "of axonal projections ever observed"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 632178.0,
      "end_time": 634439.0,
      "text": "in the central nervous system of adult mammal"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 634439.0,
      "end_time": 636983.0,
      "text": "after an injury."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 636984.0,
      "end_time": 642530.0,
      "text": "And there is a very important message"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 642530.0,
      "end_time": 646496.0,
      "text": "hidden behind this discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 646496.0,
      "end_time": 649718.0,
      "text": "They are the result of a young team"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 649718.0,
      "end_time": 652110.0,
      "text": "of very talented people:"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 652110.0,
      "end_time": 656568.0,
      "text": "physical therapists, neurobiologists, neurosurgeons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 656568.0,
      "end_time": 658766.0,
      "text": "engineers of all kinds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 658767.0,
      "end_time": 660558.0,
      "text": "who have achieved together"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 660558.0,
      "end_time": 664201.0,
      "text": "what would have been impossible by single individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 664201.0,
      "end_time": 667284.0,
      "text": "This is truly a trans-disciplinary team."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 667284.0,
      "end_time": 669472.0,
      "text": "They are working so close to each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 669472.0,
      "end_time": 672663.0,
      "text": "that there is horizontal transfer of DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 672663.0,
      "end_time": 674286.0,
      "text": "We are creating the next generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 674286.0,
      "end_time": 676526.0,
      "text": "of M.D.&#39;s and engineers"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 676527.0,
      "end_time": 678971.0,
      "text": "capable of translating discoveries all the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 678971.0,
      "end_time": 681643.0,
      "text": "from bench to bedside."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 681643.0,
      "end_time": 683649.0,
      "text": "And me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 683649.0,
      "end_time": 688196.0,
      "text": "I am only the maestro who orchestrated this beautiful symphony."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 688196.0,
      "end_time": 694999.0,
      "text": "Now, I am sure you are all wondering, aren&#39;t you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 694999.0,
      "end_time": 698763.0,
      "text": "will this help injured people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 698763.0,
      "end_time": 702655.0,
      "text": "Me too, every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 702655.0,
      "end_time": 706680.0,
      "text": "The truth is that we don&#39;t know enough yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 706680.0,
      "end_time": 710292.0,
      "text": "This is certainly not a cure for spinal cord injury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 710292.0,
      "end_time": 713260.0,
      "text": "but I begin to believe that this may lead"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 713260.0,
      "end_time": 715593.0,
      "text": "to an intervention to improve recovery"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 715593.0,
      "end_time": 718780.0,
      "text": "and people&#39;s quality of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 718780.0,
      "end_time": 721269.0,
      "text": "I would like you all"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 721269.0,
      "end_time": 724896.0,
      "text": "to take a moment and dream with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 724896.0,
      "end_time": 730790.0,
      "text": "Imagine a person just suffered a spinal cord injury."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 730791.0,
      "end_time": 733946.0,
      "text": "After a few weeks of recovery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 733946.0,
      "end_time": 736306.0,
      "text": "we will implant a programmable pump"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 736306.0,
      "end_time": 739339.0,
      "text": "to deliver a personalized pharmacological cocktail"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 739339.0,
      "end_time": 741781.0,
      "text": "directly to the spinal cord."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 741781.0,
      "end_time": 745440.0,
      "text": "At the same time, we will implant an electrode array,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 745440.0,
      "end_time": 747151.0,
      "text": "a sort of second skin"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 747151.0,
      "end_time": 750710.0,
      "text": "covering the area of the spinal cord controlling leg movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 750711.0,
      "end_time": 753977.0,
      "text": "and this array is attached to an electrical pulse generator"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 753977.0,
      "end_time": 756439.0,
      "text": "that delivers stimulations that are tailored"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 756439.0,
      "end_time": 758625.0,
      "text": "to the person&#39;s needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 758625.0,
      "end_time": 763483.0,
      "text": "This defines a personalized electrochemical neuroprosthesis"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 763483.0,
      "end_time": 766233.0,
      "text": "that will enable locomotion"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 766234.0,
      "end_time": 770281.0,
      "text": "during training with a newly designed supporting system."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 770281.0,
      "end_time": 773564.0,
      "text": "And my hope is that after several months of training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 773564.0,
      "end_time": 775727.0,
      "text": "there may be enough remodeling of residual connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 775727.0,
      "end_time": 779396.0,
      "text": "to allow locomotion without the robot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 779396.0,
      "end_time": 783174.0,
      "text": "maybe even without pharmacology or stimulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 783174.0,
      "end_time": 785708.0,
      "text": "My hope here is to be able to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 785708.0,
      "end_time": 787973.0,
      "text": "the personalized condition"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 787973.0,
      "end_time": 790636.0,
      "text": "to boost the plasticity of the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 790636.0,
      "end_time": 792166.0,
      "text": "and the spinal cord."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 792167.0,
      "end_time": 794906.0,
      "text": "And this is a radically new concept"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 794906.0,
      "end_time": 798199.0,
      "text": "that may apply to other neurological disorders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 798199.0,
      "end_time": 802737.0,
      "text": "what I termed \"personalized neuroprosthetics,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 802737.0,
      "end_time": 805761.0,
      "text": "where by sensing and stimulating neural interfaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 805761.0,
      "end_time": 809475.0,
      "text": "I implanted throughout the nervous system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 809475.0,
      "end_time": 812816.0,
      "text": "in the brain, in the spinal cord,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 812816.0,
      "end_time": 815572.0,
      "text": "even in peripheral nerves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 815572.0,
      "end_time": 818739.0,
      "text": "based on patient-specific impairments."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 818739.0,
      "end_time": 823347.0,
      "text": "But not to replace the lost function, no --"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 823347.0,
      "end_time": 826538.0,
      "text": "to help the brain help itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 826538.0,
      "end_time": 829178.0,
      "text": "And I hope this enticed your imagination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 829178.0,
      "end_time": 831740.0,
      "text": "because I can promise to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 831740.0,
      "end_time": 834317.0,
      "text": "this is not a matter of whether this revolution will occur,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 834317.0,
      "end_time": 836109.0,
      "text": "but when."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 836109.0,
      "end_time": 838342.0,
      "text": "And remember, we are only as great"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 838357.0,
      "end_time": 841942.0,
      "text": "as our imagination, as big as our dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 841942.0,
      "end_time": 843934.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 843934.0,
      "end_time": 847934.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}